---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service">
  <section style="padding: 48px 24px;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 720px;">
      <h1 style="color: var(--deep-lake); margin-bottom: 24px;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 32px;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">1. Acceptance</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        By creating an account or using Carp.Network ("the Service"), you agree to these Terms of Service.
        If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">2. The Service</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Carp.Network provides a mobile application for logging fishing catches, managing private fishing
        groups, group messaging, photo storage, and AI-powered fishing insights.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">3. Accounts</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>You must provide a valid email address to create an account.</li>
        <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials.</li>
        <li>You must be at least 16 years of age to use the Service.</li>
