        <li>Access to the Service requires an active subscription.</li>
        <li>Subscriptions are billed monthly through the Apple App Store or Google Play Store.</li>
        <li>You may cancel your subscription at any time through your app store account settings.</li>
        <li>Refunds are handled according to the policies of the respective app store.</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to change subscription pricing with 30 days' notice.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">You agree not to:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>Upload illegal, abusive, or offensive content.</li>
        <li>Attempt to access other users' data without authorisation.</li>
        <li>Reverse-engineer, scrape, or abuse the Service's APIs.</li>
        <li>Use the Service for any purpose that violates applicable laws or fishing regulations.</li>
        <li>Share login credentials or subscription access with others.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">6. Content Ownership</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        You retain ownership of all content you submit (catch reports, photos, messages). By using the
        Service, you grant us a limited licence to store, process, and display your content to other
        members of your groups as necessary to provide the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">7. Account Termination</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>You may delete your account at any time by contacting support.</li>
        <li>We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms.</li>
        <li>Upon termination, your data will be deleted in accordance with our Privacy Policy.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        The Service is provided "as is". We are not liable for any data loss, fishing outcomes,
        or damages arising from the use of the Service, to the maximum extent permitted by law.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the Service after changes
        constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">10. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:legal@carp.network">legal@carp.network</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
